OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be bright and
OL,6,Fmainly dry with some sunny spells but
OL,7,Fthere will be a scattering of light
OL,8,Fshowers. The afternoon will see any
OL,9,Fshowers die out, with longer sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Fresh southwesterly winds
OL,11,Facross Shetland at first.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome fine evening sunshine
OL,14,Fthen a mainly dry night with just the
OL,15,Fsmall chance of a light shower. Light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
