OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMostly dry and bright with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine at times, and fairly
OL,7,Flight winds. Cloud increasing later
OL,8,Fwith some light rain possible in the
OL,9,Fevening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA lot
OL,12,Fof dry weather over the next few days
OL,13,Fthough quite cloudy with the chance of
OL,14,Fa few light showers.
